== Description ==
pre Alpha State development Version of Wordpress Plugin connecting Gallery3 and Wordpress3+ maintaining compatibility to WPG2
In this experimental releas we'll integrate a g3 into a custom Post - ceacing experiments.

== Installation ==

1. Upload to your plugins folder, usually `wp-content/plugins/`
2. Activate the plugin on the plugin screen.
3. Configure the plugin on it's settings screen. Settings -> WPG3
4. Add the `< !--wpg3-->`(without the space at before the exclamation mark!) to the body of the post/page in the editors HTML mode.


== Frequently Asked Questions ==

= How do I add the contact form to a get output? =

You need to add the `< !--wpg3-->` (without the space at before the exclamation mark!) to the body of the post/page in the editors HTML mode.

